    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.41)) / (0.02 - 0.87))
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.14) + ((v2 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.02) + 0.56))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin(v1)
    tmp = (v0 / v0)
    v0 = (v0 * 0.96)
    v1 = ((0.16 - (v0 + 0.35 / tmp + 0.23)) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.56) / (v0 + 0.98 / v0 + 0.34)))
    v2 = (0.79 - (wp.sin(tmp + 0.42) - (tmp + 0.22 * tmp + 0.24)))
    data[tid] = v0
